{"tid":1680671,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"失業/Fg朋友仔入一入黎","createTime":"2019-10-29T03:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T03:39:08.000Z","uid":90618,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"029952039bb0ec38ce5bee5dd2ea23eec4b88d88","tid":1680671,"uid":90618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"想問呢到會唔會有人想了解下保險呢行，我反緊間公司aia而架請緊人，如果你有degree嘅話 人工可以由$15k-50k不等(包medical同life insurance)，人工就可以有兩種計法，一種係有底薪，另外一種就冇,呢一點就好睇你個人能力。<br />\n<br />\n我想講其實香港人對sell保險有個stereotype，成日覺得sell保險就係讀唔成書，其實而加請人sell保險好多都大學畢業，甚至我老細係3大畢業，再加上我地公司有7成人甚至master degree 畢業。<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實而加市道甘差，大部分非技術性的工種Fg人工都係12-15k，講真你做一兩年人工加幅亦不會太大。如果你係非專科畢就更加應該可以了解多的保險呢個行業，佢真係可以快速幫你人工跑贏大市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家如果有興趣知多d，可以聯絡我tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kchp1008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkchp1008&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=556f7202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kchp1008</a>"},{"pid":"7c31cdf825c466c07b419cc97114121f76d8b582","tid":1680671,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"db7375afed1b5cf6b5218e937b2fd0a1dd95eeea","tid":1680671,"uid":5378,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"走啦垃圾"},{"pid":"5d8d7166a47231cb3c022d13bf8cd91b657871d2","tid":1680671,"uid":205346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係度r下線？"},{"pid":"398c4c3259c5ea0dcdb61212340d3c6b9fb8a178","tid":1680671,"uid":107422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:15:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇人有興趣